Rating: 3
"Brutti ma buoni" are a traditional type of Italian cookie from Piemonte, made with almonds and vanilla. They are perfect with a good glass of sparkling wine or a mug of coffee or hot chocolate. Usually, the traditional recipe is with the vanilla powder. Here you can find the classic recipe: http://www.academiabarilla.com/italian-recipes/piemonte/brutti-buoni.aspx

