Rating: 2
I thought these were pretty good. I cut the sugar to 1 cup. I didn't think the dough would hold together but it did. I used the measuring teaspoon to scoop the dough and found that dipping the spoon in water helped keep the dough from sticking. I didn't mess with the shape once it was on the cookie sheet.

