Rating: 4
I have made these cookies three times in mone month. Incredible! I prefer them on the 12 mninute side so they are soft. It is so dry in Sedona the cookies can dry out quickly after they have been cooked. That's assuming that they are around long enough. They are great with cappuccino or coffee if you like biscotti. A perfect cookie/dessert for one that likes buttery desserts yet can't take the cholesterol. They're like BUTTER!

